node.text:
The Hens’ Den.❤️ 
Our coop project is coming to an end. We started building it back in May and now it’s just adding the finishing details. The hens couldn’t be happier and either could I.🐓 Entire coop tour coming soon!
.
❤️The black metal HEN DEN sign is from @redmerledesigns 
❤️ Coop paint color is Earl Gray by @magnolia Magnolia Home
❤️Solar lights from @tractorsupply 

.
.

node.text:
Heading home after a wonderful weekend in the Hamptons. We ate, we drank, took in the beautiful sites, and celebrated my sister. She is getting married in two weeks, can’t wait!👏🏼🦪🌊🦞❤️
